# Per-language golden outputs live alongside this file.
#
# Bootstrap with:
#
#   python3 idl/codegen/tests/test_convenience_generators.py --update-golden
#
# After bootstrap, this directory will contain:
#
#   golden/swift.expected
#   golden/kotlin.expected
#   golden/dart.expected
#   golden/ts.expected
#
# These are byte-checked against generator output on every test run; commit
# them after any intentional fixture or generator change. See README.md in
# this directory for the full workflow.
